             <summary>
             Creates a new account for user
             </summary>
             <remarks>
             Sample request:
            
                 POST api/account/{userId}
                 
                 {
                    FirstName : "John",
                    LastName: "Doe",
                    CompanyName: "Maxwell Enterprise Inc",
